{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Abstraction","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Abstraction","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>Abstraction in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Computer_Programming\">computer programming</a> is a way to reduce complexity and allow efficient design and implementation in complex software systems. It hides the technical complexity of systems behind simpler <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/API\">APIs</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"advantages_of_data_abstraction","title":"Advantages of Data Abstraction","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>Helps the user to avoid writing low level code.</li>\n  <li>Avoids code duplication and increases reusability.</li>\n  <li>Can change internal implementation of class independently without affecting the user.</li>\n  <li>Helps to increase security of an application or program as only important details are provided to the user.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ImplementAbstraction</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// method to set values of internal members</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">set</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> x<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>b <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> y<span class=\"t